# Testing

- Location: `src/__tests__/*.test.ts`
- Environment: jsdom (configured in `package.json`)
- Coverage excludes: `index.ts`, `types.ts`, `constants.ts`

## Singleton cleanup (required)

```typescript
afterEach(() => {
  VietnameseInput.destroyInstance();
});
```

## Test types

| Type | Target | Focus |
|------|--------|-------|
| Unit | `transform.ts`, `helpers.ts` | Multi-vowel, uppercase, tone priority, no-op |
| Integration | `VietnameseInput.ts` | Singleton, enable/disable, DOM events |

## DOM integration pattern

```typescript
const input = document.createElement('input');
document.body.appendChild(input);
input.value = 'bas';
input.selectionStart = input.selectionEnd = 3;
input.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true }));
// assert input.value
document.body.removeChild(input);
```

## All three input methods

Test Telex, VNI, and VIQR when changing `INPUT_METHODS` or transform logic.
